cu.explanation_en: Setting the integrity algorithm to the unknown enum 'nia9' will cause negotiation failure during the security negotiation phase and NAS registration rejection.

du.explanation_en: Setting hw_log_level to an invalid enum value 'invalid_hw' will cause hardware logging configuration errors and prevent proper HW log output.
du.explanation_zh: 將 hw_log_level 設定為無效的枚舉值 'invalid_hw' 會導致硬體日誌配置錯誤，並阻止正確的 HW 日誌輸出。
